{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/post/02/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Gatsby 블로그에 SEO 적용하기-(1)","coverImage":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/jpeg;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/4102bb6d44426649e0f6e7c2df74a23d/16f6e/seo_ai.jpg","srcSet":"/static/4102bb6d44426649e0f6e7c2df74a23d/398de/seo_ai.jpg 360w,\n/static/4102bb6d44426649e0f6e7c2df74a23d/6752d/seo_ai.jpg 721w,\n/static/4102bb6d44426649e0f6e7c2df74a23d/16f6e/seo_ai.jpg 1441w","sizes":"(min-width: 1441px) 1441px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/4102bb6d44426649e0f6e7c2df74a23d/30d3c/seo_ai.webp 360w,\n/static/4102bb6d44426649e0f6e7c2df74a23d/108d1/seo_ai.webp 721w,\n/static/4102bb6d44426649e0f6e7c2df74a23d/e6520/seo_ai.webp 1441w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 1441px) 1441px, 100vw"}]},"width":1441,"height":1024}}},"category":"React","tag":["SEO","Google Search Console","React","Gatsby"],"createDate":"2025-07-12","lastDate":"2025-07-12"},"html":"<p>GitHub Pages 기반의 Gatsby 블로그에 SEO를 적용하는 내용을 담은 포스트입니다.\r\n<br>\r\n관련 플러그인 설정부터 Google Search Console을 적용하는 과정을 담았습니다.</p>\n<!-- end -->\n<h1 id=\"seo란\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#seo%EB%9E%80\" aria-label=\"seo란 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>SEO란?</h1>\n<p><strong>Search Engine Optimization</strong>, 즉 '<strong>검색 엔진 최적화</strong>'라는 뜻으로,\r\n웹사이트가 구글이나 네이버 같은 검색엔진에 더 잘 노출되도록 구조와 콘텐츠를 개선하는 일련의 과정을 말합니다.</p>\n<p>아무리 좋은 웹사이트를 개발해도 검색에 노출되지 않으면 의미가 없기에 SEO는 웹사이트에 활기를 넣어주는 역할을 합니다.</p>\n<h1 id=\"seo-설정하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#seo-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"seo 설정하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>SEO 설정하기</h1>\n<h2 id=\"관련-플러그인-설치-및-설정\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B4%80%EB%A0%A8-%ED%94%8C%EB%9F%AC%EA%B7%B8%EC%9D%B8-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98-%EB%B0%8F-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95\" aria-label=\"관련 플러그인 설치 및 설정 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>관련 플러그인 설치 및 설정</h2>\n<p>검색엔진이 내 사이트의 구조를 이해하도록 도와주는 두 가지 핵심 파일은 다음과 같습니다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">sitemap.xml</code>: 어떤 페이지들이 있는지 구조적으로 정리된 파일</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">robots.txt</code>: 어떤 경로는 검색엔진이 크롤링해도 되는지 여부를 지정</li>\n</ul>\n<p>gatsby에 제공하는 각 파일에 대응되는 플러그인을 설치합니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token function\">npm</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> gatsby-plugin-sitemap gatsby-plugin-robots-txt</code></pre></div>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-config.js</code>에서 설치한 플러그인을 설정합니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">module<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>exports <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">siteMetadata</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token literal-property property\">siteUrl</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">https://lsj1206.github.io</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 사이트 도메인</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token comment\">//...</span>\r\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">plugins</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token comment\">//...</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n      <span class=\"token literal-property property\">resolve</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">gatsby-plugin-sitemap</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n      <span class=\"token literal-property property\">options</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token literal-property property\">exclude</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">/404/</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">/dev-404-page/</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n      <span class=\"token literal-property property\">resolve</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">gatsby-plugin-robots-txt</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n      <span class=\"token literal-property property\">options</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token literal-property property\">host</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">https://lsj1206.github.io</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token literal-property property\">sitemap</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">https://lsj1206.github.io/sitemap-index.xml</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token literal-property property\">policy</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\r\n          <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n            <span class=\"token literal-property property\">userAgent</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">*</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n            <span class=\"token literal-property property\">allow</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">/</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">/post/</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n            <span class=\"token literal-property property\">disallow</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">/404/</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">/dev-404-page/</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n          <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"seo-태그-적용하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#seo-%ED%83%9C%EA%B7%B8-%EC%A0%81%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"seo 태그 적용하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>SEO 태그 적용하기</h2>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">post-template.js</code>파일에서 <strong>Head export</strong>를 수정합니다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Gatsby v4 이상에서는 <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;Head></code>컴포넌트에서 <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;meta></code>정보를 설정할 수 있습니다.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">query</code>에서 가져오는 정보를 바탕으로 <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;meta></code>태그에 정보를 삽입</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">Head</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> data <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> post <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> data<span class=\"token operator\">?.</span>markdownRemark<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> frontmatter <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> post<span class=\"token operator\">?.</span>frontmatter <span class=\"token operator\">||</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> title <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> frontmatter<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>title <span class=\"token operator\">||</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Empty title..\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> description <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> post<span class=\"token operator\">?.</span>excerpt <span class=\"token operator\">||</span> title<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> url <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">https://lsj1206.github.io/post/</span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span>post<span class=\"token operator\">?.</span>fields<span class=\"token operator\">?.</span>slug<span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token string\">/</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> image <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> frontmatter<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>coverImage<span class=\"token operator\">?.</span>childImageSharp<span class=\"token operator\">?.</span>gatsbyImageData<span class=\"token operator\">?.</span>images<span class=\"token operator\">?.</span>fallback<span class=\"token operator\">?.</span>src<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\r\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>title<span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>title<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>title<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\r\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>link rel<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"canonical\"</span> href<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>url<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\r\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>meta name<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"description\"</span> content<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>description<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\r\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>meta name<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"robots\"</span> content<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"index, follow\"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\r\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token comment\">/*Open Graph 메타 태그 ...*/</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token comment\">/* Twitter Card 메타 태그 ...*/</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\r\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;meta name=\"description\"></code> 태그가 존재하는데, 해당 태그는 검색 화면에서 제목 아래에 보여지면서 해당 웹사이트의 내용을 요약해주는 역할을 합니다.</p>\n<p>해당 태그의 <code class=\"language-text\">content</code>에 본문을 삽입하게 위해 <code class=\"language-text\">query</code>를 수정하였습니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> query <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> graphql<span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">\r\n  query ($slug: String!) {\r\n    markdownRemark(fields: { slug: { eq: $slug } }) {\r\n      ...\r\n      excerpt(pruneLength: 160)\r\n      ...\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><strong>description</strong>태그에 어떤 데이터를 넣어야하는지에 대한 두가지 방안이 있었습니다. <br>\r\n하나는 <em>frontmatter</em>에 <strong>description</strong>을 추가하고 그걸 사용하는 방안과 포스트 본문의 일부를 사용하는 방안이였습니다.</p>\n<p>저는 <em>frontmatter</em>에서 description을 사용하지 않기도 하고, 글의 내용을 보여주는게 자연스럽다고 생각을 해서 Gatsby의 GraphQL에 내장되어 있는 <code class=\"language-text\">excerpt</code>필드를 사용하여 포스트 본문의 일부를 사용하는 방식으로 작성하였습니다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">excerpt</code>필드는 콘텐츠의 본문 중 일부를 자동으로 잘라내 요약해 문자열로 반환합니다.\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">pruneLength</code>옵션으로 원하는 글자 수만큼만 잘라오도록 설정하였습니다.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">module<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>exports <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n  <span class=\"token comment\">//...</span>\r\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">plugins</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token comment\">//...</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n      <span class=\"token literal-property property\">resolve</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">gatsby-transformer-remark</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n      <span class=\"token literal-property property\">options</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token comment\">//...</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token literal-property property\">excerpt_separator</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">&lt;!-- end --></span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token comment\">//...</span>\r\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>또한, <em>gatsby-transformer-remark</em> 플러그인의 <strong>excerpt_separator</strong>옵션을 추가하여 커스텀 마커로 <code class=\"language-text\">excerpt</code>의 엔드 포인트를 지정해 이중으로 description을 가져오도록 설정했습니다. <br></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/680701defd880d96d221a06020f9f875/ec5dd/ex-endpoint_used.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 13.496932515337424%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/680701defd880d96d221a06020f9f875/94563/ex-endpoint_used.webp 163w,\n/static/680701defd880d96d221a06020f9f875/647a8/ex-endpoint_used.webp 325w,\n/static/680701defd880d96d221a06020f9f875/c1dc5/ex-endpoint_used.webp 650w,\n/static/680701defd880d96d221a06020f9f875/ce5c2/ex-endpoint_used.webp 941w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/680701defd880d96d221a06020f9f875/d2f63/ex-endpoint_used.jpg 163w,\n/static/680701defd880d96d221a06020f9f875/c989d/ex-endpoint_used.jpg 325w,\n/static/680701defd880d96d221a06020f9f875/6aca1/ex-endpoint_used.jpg 650w,\n/static/680701defd880d96d221a06020f9f875/ec5dd/ex-endpoint_used.jpg 941w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/680701defd880d96d221a06020f9f875/6aca1/ex-endpoint_used.jpg\"\n            alt=\"ex-endpoint_used_image\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>사진과 같이 Markdown본문에서 지정한 엔드포인트를 사용하면 아래의 내용은 가져오지 않습니다.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>excerpt_separator</strong>와 <strong>pruneLength</strong>를 같이 사용하는 경우, <strong>excerpt_separator</strong>가 1차적으로 범위를 지정하고 이후에 텍스트의 길이를 제한합니다.<br> <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/4482341669d7eaee27a7b1ae77c4e8ea/b8284/ex-excerpt.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 47.852760736196316%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/4482341669d7eaee27a7b1ae77c4e8ea/94563/ex-excerpt.webp 163w,\n/static/4482341669d7eaee27a7b1ae77c4e8ea/647a8/ex-excerpt.webp 325w,\n/static/4482341669d7eaee27a7b1ae77c4e8ea/c1dc5/ex-excerpt.webp 650w,\n/static/4482341669d7eaee27a7b1ae77c4e8ea/1e975/ex-excerpt.webp 975w,\n/static/4482341669d7eaee27a7b1ae77c4e8ea/8a0f1/ex-excerpt.webp 985w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/4482341669d7eaee27a7b1ae77c4e8ea/d2f63/ex-excerpt.jpg 163w,\n/static/4482341669d7eaee27a7b1ae77c4e8ea/c989d/ex-excerpt.jpg 325w,\n/static/4482341669d7eaee27a7b1ae77c4e8ea/6aca1/ex-excerpt.jpg 650w,\n/static/4482341669d7eaee27a7b1ae77c4e8ea/7c09c/ex-excerpt.jpg 975w,\n/static/4482341669d7eaee27a7b1ae77c4e8ea/b8284/ex-excerpt.jpg 985w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/4482341669d7eaee27a7b1ae77c4e8ea/6aca1/ex-excerpt.jpg\"\n            alt=\"ex-excerpt_image\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>추가적으로 SEO를 적용하고 싶은 다른 페이지는 별도로 해당 파일 내에서 Head export에 태그 등을 설정해야 합니다.\r\n저는 index.js 페이지에 일부 태그를 적용했습니다.</p>\n<p>지금까지는 Gatsby 블로그 내부에서 SEO 정보를 설정하는 내용이였습니다. <br>\r\n이제부터는 외부에서 SEO가 잘 반영되고 있는지를 확인하는 과정을 설명하는 내용입니다.</p>\n<h1 id=\"google-search-console\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#google-search-console\" aria-label=\"google search console permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Google Search Console</h1>\n<p><strong>Google Search Console</strong>은 구글에서 제공하는 도구로, 내 웹사이트가 검색엔진에 어떻게 인식되고 있는지, 어떤 페이지가 <strong>검색 색인</strong>(index)에 포함되었는지를 확인하고 관리할 수 있습니다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"google-search-console에-website-등록하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#google-search-console%EC%97%90-website-%EB%93%B1%EB%A1%9D%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"google search console에 website 등록하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Google Search Console에 Website 등록하기</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"https://search.google.com/search-console/about\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Google Search Console</a>에 접속</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>속성 유형을 선택하고 Website주소 입력하기</p>\n<p><em>GitHub Pages</em>를 사용하는 경우 <strong>URL 접두어 방식</strong>을 사용해서 진행할 수 있습니다.\r\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/63dcff89ec1c4cbfaca9686253895479/307d7/GSC_setting_01.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 80.3680981595092%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/63dcff89ec1c4cbfaca9686253895479/94563/GSC_setting_01.webp 163w,\n/static/63dcff89ec1c4cbfaca9686253895479/647a8/GSC_setting_01.webp 325w,\n/static/63dcff89ec1c4cbfaca9686253895479/c1dc5/GSC_setting_01.webp 650w,\n/static/63dcff89ec1c4cbfaca9686253895479/9046c/GSC_setting_01.webp 760w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/63dcff89ec1c4cbfaca9686253895479/d2f63/GSC_setting_01.jpg 163w,\n/static/63dcff89ec1c4cbfaca9686253895479/c989d/GSC_setting_01.jpg 325w,\n/static/63dcff89ec1c4cbfaca9686253895479/6aca1/GSC_setting_01.jpg 650w,\n/static/63dcff89ec1c4cbfaca9686253895479/307d7/GSC_setting_01.jpg 760w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/63dcff89ec1c4cbfaca9686253895479/6aca1/GSC_setting_01.jpg\"\n            alt=\"gsc-setting_01\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>구분</th>\n<th>도메인 방식</th>\n<th>URL 접두어 방식</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>인증 범위</td>\n<td>전체 도메인 (<code class=\"language-text\">www</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">http</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">https</code> 모두 포함)</td>\n<td>특정 프로토콜 + 하위 경로만 (<code class=\"language-text\">https://example.com/blog/</code> 등)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>소유권 인증 방법</td>\n<td>DNS 레코드 설정 필요</td>\n<td>HTML 파일 업로드, meta 태그 등 간단한 방법 가능</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>장점</td>\n<td>서브도메인까지 포함하는 통합 관리 가능</td>\n<td>인증과 설정이 간단하고 빠름</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>단점</td>\n<td>DNS 접근 권한이 필요</td>\n<td>동일 사이트 내 다른 경로는 별도로 등록 필요</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>소유권 확인하기</p>\n<p>속성 유형을 선택한 뒤에는, 내가 해당 사이트의 진짜 소유자인지 구글에 증명하는 과정을 해야합니다.\r\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 643px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/37e3a7e31397e8ddab9a78d96ffb27df/e3f06/GSC_setting_02.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 125.76687116564416%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/37e3a7e31397e8ddab9a78d96ffb27df/94563/GSC_setting_02.webp 163w,\n/static/37e3a7e31397e8ddab9a78d96ffb27df/647a8/GSC_setting_02.webp 325w,\n/static/37e3a7e31397e8ddab9a78d96ffb27df/b1337/GSC_setting_02.webp 643w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 643px) 100vw, 643px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/37e3a7e31397e8ddab9a78d96ffb27df/d2f63/GSC_setting_02.jpg 163w,\n/static/37e3a7e31397e8ddab9a78d96ffb27df/c989d/GSC_setting_02.jpg 325w,\n/static/37e3a7e31397e8ddab9a78d96ffb27df/e3f06/GSC_setting_02.jpg 643w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 643px) 100vw, 643px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/37e3a7e31397e8ddab9a78d96ffb27df/e3f06/GSC_setting_02.jpg\"\n            alt=\"gsc-setting_02\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>GSC에서는 다양한 확인 방법을 제공하고 있는데,저는 가장 간편한 방식인 <strong>HTML 태그</strong>를 삽입하는 방식을 선택하였습니다.\r\n<code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-ssr.js</code>파일에서 해당 코드를 통해 태그를 삽입했습니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">onRenderBody</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> setHeadComponents <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n  <span class=\"token function\">setHeadComponents</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>meta name<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"google-site-verification\"</span> content<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"제공 하는 코드\"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Sitemap 제출하기</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/4297e46ba4e77132cbc3e13bf5a5294c/1dfd6/GSC_setting_03.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 41.104294478527606%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/4297e46ba4e77132cbc3e13bf5a5294c/94563/GSC_setting_03.webp 163w,\n/static/4297e46ba4e77132cbc3e13bf5a5294c/647a8/GSC_setting_03.webp 325w,\n/static/4297e46ba4e77132cbc3e13bf5a5294c/c1dc5/GSC_setting_03.webp 650w,\n/static/4297e46ba4e77132cbc3e13bf5a5294c/1e975/GSC_setting_03.webp 975w,\n/static/4297e46ba4e77132cbc3e13bf5a5294c/063bf/GSC_setting_03.webp 1300w,\n/static/4297e46ba4e77132cbc3e13bf5a5294c/ff501/GSC_setting_03.webp 1595w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/4297e46ba4e77132cbc3e13bf5a5294c/d2f63/GSC_setting_03.jpg 163w,\n/static/4297e46ba4e77132cbc3e13bf5a5294c/c989d/GSC_setting_03.jpg 325w,\n/static/4297e46ba4e77132cbc3e13bf5a5294c/6aca1/GSC_setting_03.jpg 650w,\n/static/4297e46ba4e77132cbc3e13bf5a5294c/7c09c/GSC_setting_03.jpg 975w,\n/static/4297e46ba4e77132cbc3e13bf5a5294c/01ab0/GSC_setting_03.jpg 1300w,\n/static/4297e46ba4e77132cbc3e13bf5a5294c/1dfd6/GSC_setting_03.jpg 1595w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/4297e46ba4e77132cbc3e13bf5a5294c/6aca1/GSC_setting_03.jpg\"\n            alt=\"gsc-setting_03\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\r\n앞서 Gatsby 설정에서 <code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-plugin-sitemap</code> 플러그인을 사용해 sitemap파일을 자동 생성했습니다.\r\n이 경우 보통 다음과 같은 두 종류의 파일이 생성됩니다:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">sitemap-index.xml</code> : 여러 sitemap 파일을 묶는 목차 역할을 합니다. <br>\r\n이 파일 안에는 <code class=\"language-text\">sitemap-0.xml</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">sitemap-1.xml</code> 등 실제 sitemap들이 링크되어 있습니다.</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">sitemap-0.xml</code> : 실제 URL들이 담긴 세부 sitemap 파일입니다. <br>\r\n사이트 내부의 실질적인 주소 목록이 이 파일에 기록됩니다.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>브라우저에서 <a href=\"https://%EC%82%AC%EC%9D%B4%ED%8A%B8%EC%A3%BC%EC%86%8C/sitemap-index.xml\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://사이트주소/sitemap-index.xml</a> 로 접속해서 잘 열리는지 확인하고, 구조는 정상적인지 체크한뒤에 해당 주소를 <strong>새 사이트맵 추가</strong> 입력창에 제출하면 완료됩니다.</p>\n<p>저는 제출 전, 아래 사이트를 활용하여 구조를 검증했습니다. <br>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.xml-sitemaps.com/validate-xml-sitemap.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">xml-sitemaps.com</a></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/65f04c82e61aab61f6bd8f5333b5da57/49221/sitemap-validation.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 62.576687116564415%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/65f04c82e61aab61f6bd8f5333b5da57/94563/sitemap-validation.webp 163w,\n/static/65f04c82e61aab61f6bd8f5333b5da57/647a8/sitemap-validation.webp 325w,\n/static/65f04c82e61aab61f6bd8f5333b5da57/c1dc5/sitemap-validation.webp 650w,\n/static/65f04c82e61aab61f6bd8f5333b5da57/f7ebd/sitemap-validation.webp 746w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/65f04c82e61aab61f6bd8f5333b5da57/d2f63/sitemap-validation.jpg 163w,\n/static/65f04c82e61aab61f6bd8f5333b5da57/c989d/sitemap-validation.jpg 325w,\n/static/65f04c82e61aab61f6bd8f5333b5da57/6aca1/sitemap-validation.jpg 650w,\n/static/65f04c82e61aab61f6bd8f5333b5da57/49221/sitemap-validation.jpg 746w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/65f04c82e61aab61f6bd8f5333b5da57/6aca1/sitemap-validation.jpg\"\n            alt=\"sitemap-validation\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>제출 후 대기 시간</p>\n<p>사이트맵을 제출하더라도, 색인이 바로 완료되지는 않습니다.</p>\n<p>저는 메인페이지가 색인까지 3일정도 소요되었고, sitemap은 아직도 해결되지 않았습니다.</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>이렇게 Gatsby 블로그에 SEO를 적용하고, <strong>Google Search Console</strong>까지의 과정을 정리해봤습니다.</p>\n<p>하지만 실제로는 색인 오류, canonical 주소 문제, sitemap 누락 등의 다양한 문제가 발생할 수 있습니다.<br>\r\n직접 겪었던 문제들과 그 해결 과정은 다음 포스트에서 다루겠습니다.</p>","fields":{"slug":"02"},"excerpt":"GitHub Pages 기반의 Gatsby 블로그에 SEO를 적용하는 내용을 담은 포스트입니다.\r\n\r\n관련 플러그인 설정부터 Google Search Console을 적용하는 과정을 담았습니다.","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#seo%EB%9E%80\">SEO란?</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#seo-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\">SEO 설정하기</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#%EA%B4%80%EB%A0%A8-%ED%94%8C%EB%9F%AC%EA%B7%B8%EC%9D%B8-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98-%EB%B0%8F-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95\">관련 플러그인 설치 및 설정</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#seo-%ED%83%9C%EA%B7%B8-%EC%A0%81%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\">SEO 태그 적용하기</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#google-search-console\">Google Search Console</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#google-search-console%EC%97%90-website-%EB%93%B1%EB%A1%9D%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\">Google Search Console에 Website 등록하기</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"02"}},"staticQueryHashes":["1516186060"],"slicesMap":{}}